            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Genesis 35:4",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". So Pliny says (c) in the east it was reckoned ornamental for men to wear gold in their ears. ",
